+    # And shared state must NOT have silently absorbed the framework's write
+    # as if it were the agent's edit -- it still holds what harvest_drafts
+    # actually harvested this pass (v1; v2 arrived after harvest ran).
+    assert "Body v1" in shared.read_text()
+
+    # Next pass: harvest_drafts() must pick up the mid-pass edit, because the
+    # manifest entry for it was NOT overwritten with the (unwritten) v1 hash.
